Devilcat leads his group - cloaked and non - inside.  Sitting across 
from Hydras, he glances around, noting the security 
systems.  "Indeed.  But I doubt that the element of surprise alone 
can win a war like this."  He focuses his attention on his Pred 
counterpart.  "So, what is your situation?"  It's a redundant 
question, considering the Rogues know much of the Predacon goings-on 
because of Phoenix, but it is expected.
